{"id": "1242975498758525009", "channel_id": "1242975498758525009", "type": 0, "author_id": "893347606212792350", "author_name": "xiangan3069", "author_bot": false, "content": "我今天才打到2-9，角色也還才10多20等。因為羊媽活動（2_9後才開）的各個關卡難道消耗體力是一樣的，我想知道有沒有可能帶個大佬的什麼角色助戰可以打到難度多少的活動關卡。\n\n剛剛嘗試了一下難度推薦等級60：\n帶70等雷亞\n我有150血\n第一回合敵方攻擊120×5\n我釋懷的笑了\n\n目前除了這個雷亞之外的助戰人選都是20等，所有我覺得沒什麼好挑的，請提供建議，謝謝", "timestamp": "2024-05-22T23:00:52.272000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1242975499035344917", "filename": "Screenshot_20240523_065704.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 194613, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1242975498758525009/1242975499035344917/Screenshot_20240523_065704.jpg?ex=6a006564&is=69ff13e4&hm=3a6daad16de2718c018cf594c2809c1bb60e4ec6b468c3e113d32ed2863ef511&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1242975498758525009", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "關於活動", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
